text: There's a very good chance my uni is going to get quarantined or at least close for a few weeks which is going to put a big delay on like my work as we need the software here as I only have some of it at home, what's happening at cinesite are things being delayedand that.

<https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QJWmnMNU7sI> what do you think to this shot i composited during my first year as part of a group project, thought it might be good for a showreel because of the process.
